g.text: Vite has its own internal plugins:
- css, json, assets, import.meta, web worker...
- load, prepare and resolve pwa plugin options
- prepare and expose Rollup api context
- expose pwa info using Rollup api context
- inject web manifest in html entry point
- build service worker in closeBundle hook
other options: css, json, build, ssr, rollup, env, worker...
